# Files excluded from the shinyapps.io deployment bundle.
# The deployed app needs only: app.R, R/, data-public/, renv.lock.
# data/ holds REAL team names -> excluded here so it can NEVER reach the default
# (public) deploy. The private deploy ships real names via a staging copy instead
# (see tools/deploy.R). data-public/ is intentionally NOT excluded (public default).
data/
data-raw/
tools/
img/
CLAUDE.md
reference/
rsconnect/
*.Rmd
*.html
*.csv
*.RData
*.Rproj
test_ffscrapr.r
.Renviron
.Renviron.example
.gitignore
.gitattributes
data-dictionary.md
README.md
LICENSE
